OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FFour years is a long time.
OL,8,FAugust 12th, 2021, was a horrific,
OL,9,Fheartbreaking evening in Plymouth,
OL,10,Fwhich could so easily have been
OL,11,Fprevented.
OL,13,FFive people lost their lives at the
OL,14,Fhands of an attacker who then turned
OL,15,Fhis shotgun on himself and changed the
OL,16,Fcommunity of Keyham forever.
