OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FIt later emerged that Jake Davison
OL,7,Fshould never have been granted a
OL,8,Flicence to own a weapon, given his
OL,9,Fhistory of violence and mental health
OL,10,Fissues, and multiple failings by the
OL,11,Fpolice to properly investigate his
OL,12,Fbackground and character.
OL,14,FOver the past four years there have
OL,15,Fbeen inquiries, investigations,
OL,16,Finquests and many calls for change.
