OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FPoliticians, senior coroners, police
OL,7,Fchiefs and bereaved families have
OL,8,Furged the Government to look again at
OL,9,Fwho is allowed to legally own a
OL,10,Fshotgun, and what checks should be in
OL,11,Fplace to ensure licences are only
OL,12,Fgranted to those who are safe to
OL,13,Fpossess them.
OL,15,FToday, finally, it feels as if their
OL,16,Fpleas are being answered.
OL,18,FThe Government has published guidance
OL,19,Fallowing the police to more closely
OL,20,Finterrogate applications for shotgun
OL,21,Fcertificates.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
