OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FUntil now, only one referee has been
OL,7,Fneeded to vouch for the applicant -
OL,8,Fthis will increase to two.
OL,10,FThe police should also consider
OL,11,Fwhether the applicant has a history of
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse or other violence.
OL,14,FOfficers are told they should speak to
OL,15,Fpartners and other household members
OL,16,Fto ascertain whether a gun licence is
OL,17,Fappropriate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
