OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FPolicing Minister Diana Johnson said
OL,7,Fthese changes are 'a direct response'
OL,8,Fto concerns raised by Ian Arrow,
OL,9,Fsenior coroner for Devon, following
OL,10,Fthe inquests in January 2023.
OL,12,FA representative for the families of
OL,13,Fthe Keyham victims today told ITV West
OL,14,FCountry: 'We welcome what seem to be
OL,15,Fpositive and safe additions to the
OL,16,Fstatutory guidance.'
OL,18,FIt could be argued that these checks
OL,19,Fand safeguards should already have
OL,20,Fbeen in place.
