OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FIndeed, the National Police Chiefs
OL,7,FCouncil has previously said Devon and
OL,8,FCornwall Police's firearms licensing
OL,9,Funit carried out a 'flawed assessment'
OL,10,Fof Davison's application.
OL,12,FThe police have since apologised and
OL,13,Finsisted changes have already been
OL,14,Fmade to the way they work.
OL,16,FToday's news is significant in that it
OL,17,Fformalises and legalises what the
OL,18,Fpolice should have been doing from the
OL,19,Fstart.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
