OL,3,CBereaved Plymouth families finally see
OL,4,Csign of change on gun laws
OL,6,FIt is widely accepted that the law
OL,7,Faround shotguns has been unfit for
OL,8,Fpurpose for many years, and that
OL,9,Fchange was desperately needed. But it
OL,10,Fis not clear why this change has taken
OL,11,Fso long.
